        %h3 WHO ARE WE?
        %p Nomad Credit is a financial marketplace for those underserved by other marketplaces. We aim to find the right product for international students and/or visa holders currently or planning to live in the U.S. The main visa holders we serve are F1, J1, L1 and H-1B visas. Nomad Credit allows international students and visa holders to search for education loans, education loan refinancing, personal loans, auto loans, auto insurance, student medical insurance, renters insurance and credit cards. Based upon the information provided in a search, Nomad Credit will provide the potential options for that international student or visa holder to compare.  

  
